# Dependencies and build outputs (rebuilt inside the image)
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Downloaded Câmara CSVs (large, read-only, never needed in the image)
apps/api/data

# Secrets — never ship env files into the build context
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# VCS and test artifacts
.git
**/playwright-report
**/test-results
